===Etymology===
{{PIE root|en|ḱerd}}
* First attested in the late 13th century.
* From {{inh|en|enm|acorden}}, borrowed from {{bor|en|fro|acorder}} (compare modern French {{m|fr|accord}} and {{m|en|accorder}}), from {{der|en|VL.|*accordo|*accordō, accordāre|to be heart to heart with}}, formed from {{der|en|la|ad}} + {{m|la|cor||heart}}.
* The verb is first attested in early 12th century.

